Not enough meat on hoagies tho..

name: Dan G
text: Terrible place. I ordered over $50 worth of food, the pizza came uncooked, the cheese wasn't even melted, same with the breadsticks! I called and told them, they said they would give me a credit, I called months later to use my " credit" only to find out it was a $5 credit!!! Absolutely unacceptable. Will NEVER eat here again.
